SENIOR COMPLIANCE OFFICER
Summary
Banking professional with more than 8.5 years experience in banking with the strong knowledge of banking products, services and procedures,
especially in KYC/AML/CFT/OFAC/Global sanctions/FATCA compliance sphere, who can help your company to achieve any goals while
mitigating the risks.
Skill Highlights
Excellent verbal and written communication skills with strong interpersonal Ability to work well under pressure;
skills;
Adherence to deadlines;
Strong analytical and research skills;
Detail-oriented, multitask;
Excellent team player, strong leadership abilities and team building skills;
Reliable, responsible, conscientious, easy-going;
Dynamic and self-motivated;
Demonstrated initiative and creativity in problem
Creative and result-oriented; solving;
Excellent organizational, project management and planning skills; Fast learner, eager for self-improvement.
Computer Skills
Proficiency with personal computers and pertinent mainframe systems and software packages, including MS Office Suite, AML/OFAC
monitoring software.
Languages
English (fluent), Russian (native), Belarusian (native), French (intermediate level (DELF B1), German (basic knowledge).
Professional Experience
